'''City surveillance droids''' were small, flying [[Cam droid/Legends|hovercam]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]] used by organizations such as the [[Taris Civil Authority]] and the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] to monitor [[City/Legends|cities]] on worlds such as [[Manaan/Legends|Manaan]] and [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] for crime circa [[3956 BBY]].

Earlier, when the [[Mandalorian Neo-Crusaders/Legends|Mandalorian Neo-Crusaders]] besieged Taris, a city surveillance droid attempted to issue a parking citation to a [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] [[Bomb/Legends|bomb]] that had failed to explode when it hit the planetary surface. The result was that the bomb at last did explode, incinerating the overzealous droid. Residents found this incident amusing, as the droids were generally considered a nuisance.

